---
import { siteConfig } from '../../data/siteConfig';
---

<section class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Image - 3 cols -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 reveal-scale relative">
        <div class="relative viewfinder-frame">
          <img
            src="/fotos-jd-infra/fotos jd infra/DJI_0004-1024x576.jpg.jpeg"
            alt="Bedrijfspand JD Infra drone"
            class="w-full aspect-[16/9] object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Floating stat card - light version -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 right-4 sm:right-8 bg-white border border-secondary-100 p-6 sm:p-8 hidden sm:block z-10 shadow-xl">
          <span class="block font-heading font-black text-5xl text-accent-400" data-counter="2006" data-counter-type="year">2006</span>
          <span class="text-secondary-400 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-heading mt-1 block">Opgericht</span>
          <div class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-accent-400/40 mt-3"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content - 2 cols -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 reveal">
        <span class="text-accent-500 font-heading font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 block">Over ons</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-primary-500 leading-[0.9] mb-6">
          JD Infra
        </h2>
        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-accent-400 mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-secondary-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          JD Infra aannemingsbedrijf is in 2006 opgericht en in de loop van de jaren uitgegroeid tot een vakkundig infrabedrijf met 12 tot 15 vaste medewerkers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          In maart 2018 zijn wij verhuisd naar ons nieuwe bedrijfspand op industrieterrein Karreveld te Koudekerke. Van hieruit bedienen wij heel Zeeland.
        </p>

        <a href="/over-ons/" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-accent-400 hover:bg-accent-300 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-none font-heading font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider transition-all duration-300">
          Lees meer
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
